msgid "Probe"
msgstr "Sonda"

#: ospy\templates\sensor.html:892
msgid "controls the program"
msgstr "řídí program"

#: ospy\templates\sensor.html:893
msgid "Mark the required programs for adjusting the program run time."
msgstr "Označte požadované programy pro úpravu doby běhu programu."

#: ospy\templates\sensor.html:901
msgid "Probe Calibration for 100%"
msgstr "Kalibrace sondy pro 100%"

#: ospy\templates\sensor.html:902 ospy\templates\sensor.html:907
msgid ""
"If necessary, we can adjust the value from the sensor from 0.00 to +6.00"
msgstr "V případě potřeby můžeme nastavit hodnotu ze senzoru od 0,00 do +6,00"

#: ospy\templates\sensor.html:906
msgid "Probe Calibration for 0%"
msgstr "Kalibrace sondy pro 0%"

#: ospy\templates\sensor.html:911
msgid "Probe logic is reversed"
msgstr "Logika sondy je otočena"

#: ospy\templates\sensor.html:912
msgid ""
"If we mark this field, the logic of the probe will be reversed. This means, "
"for example, that 0V from the probe is 100% and 3V is 0% humidity. Otherwise "
"the logic is straightforward (0V is 0% and 3V is 100%)"
msgstr ""
"Pokud je zaškrtnuto toto pole je otočena logika sondy. To například znamená, "
"že 0V ze sondy je 100% a 3V je 0% vlhkosti. Jinak je logika přímá (0V je 0% "
"a 3V je 100%)"

#: ospy\templates\sensor.html:916
msgid "Probe label"
msgstr "Popisek sondy"

#: ospy\templates\sensor.html:917
msgid "Enter a label for your probe identification"
msgstr "Zadejte popisek pro identifikaci sondy"

#: ospy\templates\sensor.html:921
msgid "Show in footer"
msgstr "Zobrazit v zápatí na hl. stránce"

#: ospy\templates\sensor.html:922
msgid "Show data from probe in footer on home page"
msgstr "Zobrazit data ze sondy v zápatí na domovské stránce"

#: ospy\templates\sensor.html:939
msgid ""
"To connect 16 pcs of humidity probes, it is necessary to connect 4 pcs of "
"the ADS1115 circuit to the IIC bus to the multisensor board (1 pc always for "
"4 A/D inputs). Each ADS1115 circuit has its own IIC address set (0x48, 0x49, "
"0x4A, 0x4B)."
msgstr ""
"Pro připojení 16 ks sond vlhkosti je nutné připojit 4 ks obvodu ADS1115 ke "
"sběrnici IIC k desce multisnímače (1 ks vždy pro 4 A/D vstupy). Každý okruh "
"ADS1115 má vlastní sadu adres IIC (0x48, 0x49, 0x4A, 0x4B)."

#: ospy\templates\sensor.html:954
msgid ""
"Cannot be used for these programs: weekly advanced, custom, weekly weather! "
"These programs will not appear in the menu and cannot be selected."
msgstr ""
"Nelze použít pro tyto programy: týdenní pokročilé, vlastní, týdenní počasí! "
"Tyto programy se nezobrazí v nabídce a nelze je vybrat."

#: ospy\templates\sensor.html:954
msgid ""
"If the program does not have a days marked, it will not start (neither by "
"the \"run now\" button in the programs, nor by this sensor)!"
msgstr ""
"Pokud program nemá označené dny, nespustí se (ani tlačítkem \"spustit nyní\" "
"v programech, ani tímto senzorem)!"

#: ospy\templates\sensor.html:954
msgid ""
"Select the program you want to activate during the event (closed/open). A "
"switch connected to the multisensor board."
msgstr ""
"Vyberte programy, který chcete během akce aktivovat (sepnutí/uvolnění). "
"Přepínače jsou připojeny k desce multisnímače."

#: ospy\templates\sensor.html:954
msgid ""
"The selected program that we want to run with this does not have to be "
"enabled in the programs, but it must have set all days when we want the "
"program to run."
msgstr ""
"Vybraný program, který chceme spustit nemusí být v programech povolen, ale "
"musí mít nastavené všechny dny, kdy chceme program spustit."

